dct_description_sm: Map of Algiers, with insets of forts and harbor; relief shown by hachures. Pictorial view at head of map, with title: Ansicht der auf dem Hafendamm errichteten Batterien und Gebäude. Map shows houses of English and U.S. consuls and palace of dey. In top margin: Zu pag. 73, 3te Jahrgang, Tab. XIX.
